    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> soy sauce</strong> with the juice of your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>grated garlic</strong> and <strong>grated ginger</strong> in a bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>Vietnamese-style marinade</strong></p>",
