    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>radishes</strong> (as finely as you can)</p><p>Chop your <strong>cucumber </strong>in half lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Peel your <strong>carrot[s]</strong>, then continue to peel lengths until you end up with a pile of carrot ribbons</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stems and finely slice them, discard the stems</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
