    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>marinated haddock</strong> along with any <strong>remaining marinade</strong> from the bowl and cook for 5 min turning half way or until cooked through – this is your <strong>Vietnamese-style haddock</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
