      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> Vietnamese-style haddock </strong>with the <strong>sticky rice</strong> and the <strong>crunchy salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over your <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds </strong>and<strong> chopped mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
